Value PROTOCOL (\S+)
Value RECV_Q (\d+)
Value SEND_Q (\d+)
Value LOCAL_ADDRESS (\S+)
Value FOREIGN_ADDRESS (\S+)
Value STATE (\S*)
Value PID (\d+)
Value PROGRAM (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Proto\s+Recv-Q\s+Send-Q\s+Local Address\s+Foreign Address\s+State\s+PID/Program name\s*$$
